OL,5,G1200 Traffic Cops
OL,6,     FWith reoffending rates on the rise
OL,7,     Fin the UK, we follow the Traffic
OL,8,     FCops as they are increasingly
OL,9,     Ffaced with seasoned criminals,
OL,10,     Fexperienced at evading the law.
OL,11,G1300 Traffic Cops
OL,12,     FWith over 1000 people killed or
OL,13,     Fseriously injured by uninsured,
OL,14,     Funlicensed or disqualified drivers
OL,15,     Feach year, Derbyshire's traffic
OL,16,     Fcops set out to tackle illegal and
OL,17,     Fdangerous drivers.
