OL,5,G2300 Skin A&E
OL,6,     FDr Toby Nelson faces the prospect
OL,7,     Fof removing a lipoma that's
OL,8,     Funderneath a patient's tattoo. Dr
OL,9,     FNatalia Spierings aims to make a
OL,10,     Fgroom-to-be picture perfect for
OL,11,     Fhis wedding photos.
